name: Blood Raider Chemosh Blueprint Armored Cache
description:
This armored and electromagnetically hardened data cache is normally integrated into the Blood Raider Covenant's shipyard facilities, providing a high level of security and protection from corruption while building Chemosh-class Dreadnoughts.

These armored caches have a good chance of surviving the destruction of the facility they are installed in. If recovered by suitable ships, the caches can be accessed and the Chemosh blueprint data recovered.
